data.description: It's a GEM! Great Investment property for Traveling Nurses or Doctors near Medical Center! Quiet neighborhood near medical center. 3017 square ft, 4 bedrooms, 2 primary suites, 3 living areas. Fireplace, office/study, fine wood laminate flooring. Covered patio with grill. Mature oak trees, occasional deer sightings. Spacious lots. Circular drive, additional parking, covered RV/boat parking. Paradise in medical center area.
